prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style senior turtle, wearing a tiny, brightly colored party hat slightly askew, comically struggles to blow out a single, gigantic, wobbly candle on a small cupcake. The turtle's cheeks are puffed out with great effort, and its eyes are wide with exertion. In the center, above the scene, the text "happy birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable, handwritten cursive script. The entire design is a flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style, featuring soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the figures, creating a lighthearted and humorous feel.
